Readme

This project is about getting the next bus(es) from IITG to Guwahati City and vice versa.
It shows max 3 buses available on current day.

Features:
>Simple interface
>No input required, just open the app and you're done.
>Shows you the Bus no. and its Route, you can check-out the nearest drop-off point from your destination and pick-up points.
> Accessible and Readable in Mobile devices, minimum you need is GPRS Connectivity (to view the site)

To be implemented:
>A better GUI
>capability to view more buses (after 3) And to check the buses on specific date
>incorporation with Academic Calender, to include the other holiday buses. 